From: Jing Zhang <jingzhangos@google.com>

Update sysreg.h to align with the canonical kernel source now that
there's a header that approximates the generated sysreg definitions.
While at it, fix KVM selftests that use macros which suffered a rename.

Signed-off-by: Jing Zhang <jingzhangos@google.com>
Reviewed-by: Marc Zyngier <maz@kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Oliver Upton <oliver.upton@linux.dev>
